00:52:39.338 --> 00:52:40.046
Amen.

00:52:40.046 --> 00:52:45.296
I appreciate you praying with me today.

00:52:45.296 --> 00:52:48.337
Jesus is the Healer.

00:52:48.337 --> 00:53:01.464
If you've never been to the channel before, click the like and subscribe buttons.

00:53:01.464 --> 00:53:16.480
I'll never ask you for anything or private message you for crypto or money.

00:53:16.480 --> 00:53:22.400
Don't fall victim to that; it's not me.

00:53:22.400 --> 00:53:30.775
I'm not going to call you and give you a prophetic word.

00:53:30.775 --> 00:53:35.800
These people are trying to steal money.

00:53:42.499 --> 00:53:47.413
I had to say that because these relentless people are stealing my stuff.

00:53:47.413 --> 00:53:59.235
We'll be back tomorrow, and I'll try to get Dianne on here with me to share her testimony.

00:53:59.235 --> 00:54:01.880
Click the notification bell.

00:54:04.453 --> 00:54:08.666
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:54:08.666 --> 00:54:10.896
Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:54:11.112 --> 00:54:18.344
We intercede for your finances and for God to do something big.

00:54:29.339 --> 00:54:32.359
It's exciting to see what the Lord is doing through this channel.

00:54:33.959 --> 00:54:37.983
I'm believing for a million-person prayer army.

00:54:37.983 --> 00:54:54.714
Think about what that is to the kingdom of darkness—knocking the devil in the teeth.

00:54:54.714 --> 00:54:58.480
He flees in terror.

00:54:58.480 --> 00:55:06.617
God bless you all, and we will see you tomorrow.

00:55:06.617 --> 00:55:08.025
Bye-bye.
